import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';

import Offcanvas from 'react-bootstrap/Offcanvas';
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import './css/main.css';

function NavbarComponent() {

                    <Nav.Link href="/ProfessionalExperience">Professional Experience</Nav.Link>

                    <NavDropdown

                      <NavDropdown.Item href="/ELearningResources">HTML / CSS</NavDropdown.Item>

      {['sm'].map((expand) => (
        <Navbar key={expand} expand={expand} className="mb-3 navbar-light">
          <Container fluid>
            <Navbar.Brand href="#" className="navLink">Yusuf's Portfolio</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls={`offcanvasNavbar-expand-${expand}`} />
            <Navbar.Offcanvas
              id={`offcanvasNavbar-expand-${expand}`}
              aria-labelledby={`offcanvasNavbarLabel-expand-${expand}`}
              placement="end"
            >
              <Offcanvas.Header closeButton>
                <Offcanvas.Title id={`offcanvasNavbarLabel-expand-${expand}`}>
                  Offcanvas
                </Offcanvas.Title>
              </Offcanvas.Header>
              <Offcanvas.Body>

                <Nav variant="underline" defaultActiveKey="/" >
                  {/* // // onSelect={(selectedKey) => 
                  // console.log(`You just selected ${selectedKey} !`)
                  // Nav.activeKey = selectedKey
                  //}> */}
                
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link eventKey="/">Home</Nav.Link>
                  </Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link href="/Projects" eventKey="/Projects">Projects</Nav.Link>
                  </Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link eventKey="Contact" >Contact</Nav.Link>
                  </Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link eventKey="ProfessionalExperience">Professional Experience</Nav.Link>
                  </Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <Nav.Link eventKey="/Qualifications">Qualifications</Nav.Link>
                  </Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Item>
                    <NavDropdown
                      title="e-Learning Resources"
                    >

                        JavaScript
                      </NavDropdown.Item>
                      <NavDropdown.Divider />
                      <NavDropdown.Item href="/ELearningResources">
                        React
                      </NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                  </Nav.Item>
                </Nav>

              </Offcanvas.Body>
            </Navbar.Offcanvas>
          </Container>
        </Navbar>
      ))}
    </>
  );

export default NavbarComponent;
